---
// FinalCTA - Bottom call-to-action section
---

<section class="cta-section section">
  <div class="container container--narrow">
    <div class="reveal">
      <div class="section-label" style="justify-content: center;">
        <span style="display: block; width: 24px; height: 1px; background: var(--color-primary);"></span>
        The Clock is Running
        <span style="display: block; width: 24px; height: 1px; background: var(--color-primary);"></span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="cta-title">
        The old world is ending.<br/>
        <span style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--color-primary), var(--color-tertiary)); -webkit-background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent; background-clip: text;">The new one needs you.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="cta-body">
        The nucleation doesn't require a majority. It requires the right people, in the right place, doing the right first thing. Florence wasn't built by everyone — it was started by a few who believed the art was worth the risk.
      </p>
      <a href="#volunteer" class="btn btn--primary btn--large">
        Become a Founder of Zone Zero
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
